<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$chu-fen-42" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/chu-fen-42" class="zg-link" title="楚芬">楚芬</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$liutao-95" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/liutao-95" class="zg-link" title="liutao">liutao</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zheng-nan-gua-88" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zheng-nan-gua-88" class="zg-link" title="郑楠瓜">郑楠瓜</a></span>
